525fb9fc50db3e6410eda5869b311809d","tid":460781,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最落力打貪既雜總原來係最貪污嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五毛：習大大家人 唔係佢貧<br />\n<br />\n支共傳統  全家一人從政  共他人從商<br />\n從政的要乾淨 好勃起來<br />\n<br />\n唔講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dc8909407ed38574f10b96972464b23b466595","tid":460781,"uid":37735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最落力打貪既雜總原來係最貪污嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五毛：習大大家人 唔係佢貧<br />\n<br />\n不過支共有一個傳統  <br />\n全家一人從政  共他人從商 是唔是一個唔一定 不過有人從政 有人從商<br />\n呢個道理 我看勃起來 果次 唔知邊個講<br />\n<br />\n從政的要乾淨  衰野同佢無關<br />\n但利用權勢為自己兄弟攞著數<br />\n<br />\n某程度都岩 勃起來 令計劃全部都有兄弟經商<br />\n<br />\n所謂鄧小平刑不上常委 免死 唔係為左減低政治殘忍 是一種妥協  輸左都有得貪 唔會死  好像薄瓜瓜 依家一樣風流快活<br />\n<br />\n我講過支那共產黨全部都係狗種 <br />\n劣種血脈 有條5毛話我唔識野 <br />\n心諗佢點看呢個post"},{"pid":"80d637ed61f90032e68746dc0f935708cc146b98","tid":460781,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"1xk vs 新x安"},{"pid":"c4b6fd7751c5f9e740ffbbf0648c233c395d73a2","tid":460781,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"公屋數量封頂<br />\n轉綠置居<br />\n穩樓市 谷樓市"},{"pid":"94dd19461eb834b578c07cd3b6b16e4dc54059b5","tid":460781,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:18:28.000Z","msg":"香港=支共洗黑錢天堂"},{"pid":"80613cb02a66596b4d45bb3a1aa5bb4a9bb7e22d","tid":460781,"uid":595